QUARTO for iPhone and iPad

This is the full source and resource listing for an OpenGL based "Quarto" 
game I wrote for iOS.  Note that the "Quarto" name and concept are 
trademarked and copyrighted so this project is posted for informative purposes only.

Redistribution of the non-source code files contained here-in is 
prohibited.  They are supplied so that you may download and compile the 
project in its entirety.

Distribution of the full source code will likely incur the wrath of the 
copyright holders and we bear no responsibility for your actions in this 
regard.  You have been warned.

Usage of the source code (in part) is acceptable and encouraged.

